text: Safet Gjici (born 30 April 1972 in Kukës) is an Albanian businessman who is the CEO of EuroGjici Security and Kevin Construction. He is also the president of Albanian Superliga football club FK Kukësi. He was the Socialist Party candidate in the municipality of Kamëz in the 2015 local elections, but he lost to the Democratic Party candidate Xhelal Mziu.Bashkia KamëzPrefekt i Kukësit ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Albanian businesspeople Category:Living people Category:People from Kukës Category:People from Kamëz Category:University of Tirana alumni Category:Socialist Party of Albania politicians
